    <url type="bugtracker">https://github.com/MuntashirAkon/SlobDict/issues</url>
    <summary>A modern, lightweight GTK 4 dictionary app for Linux</summary>
    <description>
        <p>Slob Dictionary is an application with a polished GTK 4 interface for exploring slob-formatted dictionaries on Linux.</p>
        <p>Key features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Fsst and simultaneous lookup across multiple dictionary files</li>
            <li>Persistent lookup history to revisit entries effortlessly</li>
            <li>Bookmarks for saving favorite definitions and terms</li>
            <li>Native light/dark mode following your GNOME desktop theme</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Note: The application requires network access for loading remote contents, but it is disabled by default for privacy.</p>
    </description>
